snippet: A spaceship carrying cargo bound for the International Space Station is on course despite the disintegration of one of its rocket engines shortly after liftoff on Sunday night.
abstract: Spaceship carrying cargo bound for the International Space Station is on course despite experiencing engine trouble shortly after liftoff.
lead_paragraph: A spaceship carrying cargo bound for the International Space Station is on course despite the disintegration of one of its rocket engines shortly after liftoff on Sunday night.
